                Make sure to browse our products !
            </p>
            <p class="block text-center">
                <a href="#new" class="btn">Products</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="block">
                Cheers,<br><br>
                Your friendly <em>Admin</em>
